that we can go?

01:09:06.790 --> 01:09:08.990
- Okay.
- Yeah?

01:09:16.600 --> 01:09:18.270
So...

01:09:18.300 --> 01:09:20.670
how did it go?

01:09:22.109 --> 01:09:23.609
